sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant Stripe
    participant Database
    participant Shiprocket

    Customer->>Frontend: Initiate Checkout
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /v1/payments/checkout
    Backend->>Database: Fetch Products
    Database-->>Backend: Product Data
    Backend->>Backend: Calculate Totals
    Backend->>Stripe: Create Payment Intent
    Stripe-->>Backend: Client Secret
    Backend->>Database: Save Order & Payment
    Backend-->>Frontend: Client Secret
    Frontend->>Stripe: Complete Payment
    Stripe-->>Frontend: Payment Success
    Frontend->>Customer: Show Success

    Stripe->>Backend: Webhook: payment_intent.succeeded
    Backend->>Database: Update Payment Status
    Backend->>Database: Update Order Status
    Backend->>Database: Reduce Inventory
    Backend->>Shiprocket: Book Shipment
    Shiprocket-->>Backend: Tracking Number
    Backend->>Database: Save Shipment Details
    Backend->>Customer: Send Email Notification
